---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import DynamicPageBlocks from '../components/DynamicPageBlocks.astro';
import { getZeffyDonationUrl } from '../config/siteLinks';

const zeffyDonateUrl = getZeffyDonationUrl();
---

<BaseLayout
	title="Surf Del Mar Festival"
	description="Celebrating the sport and the culture. Preserving the stories and the spirit. Del Mar Historical Society Surfing Festival."
	pageKey="home"
>
	<!-- Hero: full-screen with sunset/surfer background -->
	<section class="hero-long" aria-label="Surf Del Mar Festival">
		<img
			src="/surfdelmar.png"
			alt=""
			class="hero-long-bg"
			width="1200"
			height="800"
			fetchpriority="high"
			data-original-src="/surfdelmar.png"
			onerror="this.onerror=null;this.src=this.getAttribute('data-original-src')||'/surfdelmar.png';"
		/>
		<div class="hero-long-overlay"></div>
		<div class="hero-long-content">
			<h1 class="hero-long-title" data-editable="home.hero.title">Surf Del Mar Festival</h1>
			<p class="hero-long-subtitle" data-editable="home.hero.subtitle">October 8–11, 2026</p>
			<div class="hero-long-divider"></div>
			<p class="hero-long-tagline" data-editable="home.hero.tagline1">Celebrating the Sport and the Culture</p>
			<p class="hero-long-tagline" data-editable="home.hero.tagline2">Preserving the Stories and the Spirit</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Reunion: two-column -->
	<section class="reunion-section">
		<div class="reunion-container">
			<div class="reunion-col reunion-col-image">
				<div class="reunion-poster-wrap">
					<img src="/Poster.webp" alt="Surf Del Mar Festival poster by John Van Hamersveld" class="reunion-poster" width="600" height="900" />
					<a href="https://www.post-future.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="reunion-poster-btn">See more of John Van Hamersveld's work.</a>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="reunion-col reunion-col-text">
				<p class="reunion-body" data-editable="home.reunion.body">
					SURF DEL MAR FESTIVAL is more than a festival—it's a Reunion, decades in the making. It brings together generations of surfers, storytellers, artists, musicians, authors and filmmakers for a one-of-a-kind event celebrating the sport, the culture, the legacy and the surfing history of Del Mar and the surrounding communities.
				</p>
				<p class="reunion-join" data-editable="home.reunion.join">JOIN US OVER FOUR UNFORGETTABLE DAYS</p>
				<div class="calendar-callout">
					<p class="calendar-callout-dates" data-editable="home.reunion.dates">October 8–11, 2026 – Del Mar, California</p>
				</div>
				<p class="reunion-tagline" data-editable="home.reunion.tagline">Come Be A Part Of The History and The Fun When Surfers Come Together Again</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Don Hansen Tribute -->
	<section class="hansen-section">
		<div class="hansen-container">
			<h2 class="hansen-heading">A Tribute to Don Hansen</h2>

			<div class="hansen-content">
				<div class="hansen-photo-frame">
					<img src="/hanson.png" alt="Don Hansen" class="hansen-photo" width="942" height="910" />
					<span class="photo-caption">Don Hansen (1936–2026)</span>
				</div>

				<p class="hansen-body">Donald Hansen, an entrepreneur, athlete and adventurer whose life stretched far beyond any one calling, passed away on March 28th, 2026 at the age of 89.</p>

				<p class="hansen-body">To write about Don Hansen is to write about motion: prairie wind, Pacific swell, open sky, mountain trails and the forward pull of a man who never stopped testing the edges of life. Don leaves behind a legacy rooted not only in adventure, but in kindness, mentorship and family.</p>

				<p class="hansen-body">Born in 1936 in Aberdeen, South Dakota, to Fred and Violet Hansen, Don was raised in nearby Redfield where he spent his youth hunting, fishing, working and later dreaming of California. It was in his early years on the prairie that Don was introduced to California, where he discovered the sport that would forever mark his path: surfing. In 1960, Don founded Hansen Surfboards near Cardiff Reef in Encinitas. The shop became one of the best-known names in California surf culture. For generations of surfers, skaters, skiers and local families, Hansen's was a gathering place and Don was its heart. He had an instinct not only for business, but for people. He helped sponsor top surfers, mentored young workers and earned the respect of the broader surfing world.</p>

				<p class="hansen-body">Don chased challenge everywhere. He surfed big Hawaiian waves when that frontier was still young. In those Pacific swells, Don found his Kulia (koo-lee-ah), stepping into something bigger, pushing past comfort and the thrill of chasing adventure.</p>

				<p class="hansen-body">That appetite for challenge never stopped at the shoreline; it carried him into the open sky. As captain of the Airfreight skydiving team, he helped lead a squad that won national titles and set world records in ten-man speed star competition. Later, on Montana mountain trails, Don "let her buck"–a phrase once used by World War I soldiers from Montana as they charged into battle–and he brought that same spirit to the mountains while living in Big Sky, taking up team roping with enthusiasm and grit.</p>

				<p class="hansen-body">What set Don apart was not just his willingness to take risks, but his willingness to care. He carried a strong spirit, a memorable sense of humor and an infectious laugh. Don moved through life with faith and gratitude, meeting moments with humor and believing in people before they fully believed in themselves.</p>
			</div>
			<img src="/surfboards.png" alt="Surfboards" class="hansen-surfboards" width="1920" height="1080" />
			<div class="hansen-polaroid">
				<img src="/hansensurfing.png" alt="Hansen surfing" class="hansen-polaroid-img" width="1000" height="752" />
				<div class="tape-element"></div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<DynamicPageBlocks pageKey="home" />

	<!-- Support / donate (Zeffy); copy editable when logged in as admin -->
	<section class="support-section" aria-labelledby="support-heading">
		<div class="support-inner">
			<h2 id="support-heading" class="support-heading" data-editable="home.support.heading">Support Surf Del Mar Festival</h2>
			<p class="support-text" data-editable="home.support.body">
				Help us keep this festival and our coastal heritage programs going. Donations are processed securely through Zeffy.
			</p>
			<a
				href={zeffyDonateUrl}
				class="btn-support"
				target="_blank"
				rel="noopener noreferrer"
			>
				Donate with Zeffy
			</a>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Final CTA -->
	<section class="cta-section">
		<a href="/schedule/" class="btn-schedule">VIEW FULL EVENT SCHEDULE</a>
	</section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
	/* --- Coastal Vintage palette (use vars where existing) --- */
	.hero-long {
		position: relative;
		min-height: 80vh;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		background-color: var(--color-ink);
		text-align: center;
		color: var(--color-cream);
		overflow: hidden;
	}

	.hero-long-bg {
		position: absolute;
		inset: 0;
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
		object-fit: cover;
		object-position: center center;
		filter: brightness(1.12);
		z-index: 0;
	}

	.hero-long-overlay {
		position: absolute;
		inset: 0;
		background: linear-gradient(0deg, rgba(30,46,46,0.6) 0%, rgba(30,46,46,0.25) 50%, transparent 100%);
		z-index: 1;
		pointer-events: none;
	}

	.hero-long-content {
		position: relative;
		z-index: 2;
		max-width: 720px;
		padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
	}

	.hero-long-title {
		font-family: var(--font-display);
		font-size: clamp(3rem, 10vw, 5.5rem);
		font-weight: 700;
		letter-spacing: 0.02em;
		margin: 0 0 0.25rem 0;
		line-height: 1.05;
		text-shadow: 0 2px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
	}

	.hero-long-subtitle {
		font-family: var(--font-body);
		font-size: clamp(2.25rem, 7.5vw, 4.25rem);
		font-weight: 600;
		letter-spacing: 0.45em;
		margin: 0 0 1.25rem 0;
		opacity: 0.95;
		text-shadow: 0 1px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
	}

	.hero-long-divider {
		width: 120px;
		height: 2px;
		background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(229,240,242,0.9), transparent);
		margin: 0 auto 1.5rem auto;
	}

	.hero-long-tagline {
		font-family: var(--font-display);
		font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 4.5vw, 2.25rem);
		font-weight: 500;
		margin: 0 0 0.35rem 0;
		opacity: 0.95;
		text-shadow: 0 1px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
	}

	/* --- Reunion two-column --- */
	.reunion-section {
		background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--color-cream) 0%, var(--color-sand) 50%, var(--color-foam) 100%);
		padding: 4rem 2rem;
	}

	.reunion-container {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
		gap: 3rem;
		align-items: center;
		max-width: 1100px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.reunion-container {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			gap: 2rem;
		}
		.reunion-col-image {
			order: 1;
		}
		.reunion-col-text {
			order: 2;
		}
	}

	.reunion-poster-wrap {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		justify-content: center;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 1.25rem;
	}

	.reunion-poster-btn {
		display: inline-block;
		padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
		font-family: var(--font-body);
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		letter-spacing: 0.02em;
		color: var(--color-cream);
		background: var(--color-ink);
		border-radius: 50px;
		text-decoration: none;
		transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
	}

	.reunion-poster-btn:hover {
		transform: translateY(-2px);
		box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
	}

	.reunion-poster {
		width: 100%;
		max-width: 420px;
		height: auto;
		display: block;
		border-radius: 6px;
		box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.18), 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
		transform: rotate(-2deg);
		transition: transform 0.35s ease, box-shadow 0.35s ease;
	}

	.reunion-poster-wrap:hover .reunion-poster {
		transform: rotate(0deg);
		box-shadow: 0 24px 56px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
	}

	.reunion-heading {
		font-family: var(--font-display);
		font-size: clamp(1.85rem, 4vw, 2.35rem);
		font-weight: 600;
		color: var(--color-ink);
		margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
		line-height: 1.2;
	}

	.reunion-body {
		font-family: var(--font-body);
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		color: var(--color-ink);
		line-height: 1.75;
		margin: 0 0 1.5rem 0;
		max-width: 48ch;
	}

	.reunion-join {
		font-family: var(--font-body);
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		letter-spacing: 0.12em;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		color: var(--color-ink);
		margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
		line-height: 1.4;
	}

	.reunion-tagline {
		font-family: var(--font-display);
		font-size: 1.15rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		color: var(--color-ink);
		line-height: 1.45;
		margin: 1.25rem 0 0 0;
		max-width: 42ch;
	}

	.calendar-callout {
		background: rgba(204,228,232,0.75);
		border-left: 4px solid #c9a227;
		padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 0 10px 10px 0;
		box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
	}

	.calendar-callout-label {
		font-family: var(--font-body);
		font-size: 0.8rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.1em;
		color: var(--color-sepia);
		margin: 0 0 0.35rem 0;
	}

	.calendar-callout-dates {
		font-family: var(--font-display);
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		color: var(--color-ink);
		margin: 0;
		line-height: 1.35;
	}

	/* --- Don Hansen Tribute: Editorial Style --- */
	.hansen-section {
		background: var(--color-cream);
		padding: 6rem 2rem;
		border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
	}

	.hansen-container {
		max-width: 900px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.hansen-heading {
		font-family: var(--font-display);
		font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
		font-weight: 600;
		color: var(--color-ink);
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
		text-align: center;
		position: relative;
		line-height: 1.2;
	}

	.hansen-heading::after {
		content: '';
		display: block;
		width: 60px;
		height: 3px;
		background: #c9a227;
		margin: 1rem auto 0;
	}

	.hansen-content {
		display: block;
	}

	.hansen-content::after {
		content: '';
		display: table;
		clear: both;
	}

	.hansen-photo-frame {
		float: left;
		width: 40%;
		margin: 0 3rem 2rem 0;
	}

	.hansen-photo {
		width: 100%;
		height: auto;
		border-radius: 4px;
		box-shadow: 15px 15px 0px var(--color-sand);
		border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
	}

	.photo-caption {
		display: block;
		font-family: var(--font-body);
		font-size: 0.8rem;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.1em;
		margin-top: 1.5rem;
		padding-left: 0.75rem;
		color: var(--color-sepia);
	}

	.hansen-body {
		font-family: var(--font-body);
		font-size: 1.15rem;
		line-height: 1.8;
		color: var(--color-ink);
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	.hansen-surfboards {
		display: block;
		width: calc(100% + 8rem);
		margin-left: -4rem;
		height: auto;
		clear: both;
		margin-top: 1.25rem;
		border-radius: 8px;
	}

	.hansen-polaroid {
		position: relative;
		width: 55%;
		margin: 2rem auto 1rem;
		padding: 14px 14px 44px;
		background: #fff;
		box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.13), 0 4px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
		transform: rotate(1.5deg);
		transition: transform 0.35s ease, box-shadow 0.35s ease;
		clear: both;
	}

	.hansen-polaroid:hover {
		transform: rotate(0deg) scale(1.01);
		box-shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.16);
	}

	.hansen-polaroid .tape-element {
		position: absolute;
		top: -14px;
		left: 50%;
		transform: translateX(-50%) rotate(-2deg);
		width: 100px;
		height: 30px;
		background: rgba(184, 220, 228, 0.55);
		backdrop-filter: blur(2px);
		box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
		z-index: 2;
	}

	.hansen-polaroid-img {
		display: block;
		width: 100%;
		height: auto;
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.hansen-polaroid {
			width: 80%;
		}
	}

	/* --- Support / donate --- */
	.support-section {
		background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--color-sand) 0%, var(--color-cream) 100%);
		padding: 3.5rem 2rem;
		text-align: center;
		border-top: 1px solid rgba(26, 46, 46, 0.08);
		border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(26, 46, 46, 0.06);
	}

	.support-inner {
		max-width: 560px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.support-heading {
		font-family: var(--font-display);
		font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.25rem);
		font-weight: 600;
		color: var(--color-ink);
		margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
		line-height: 1.2;
	}

	.support-text {
		font-family: var(--font-body);
		font-size: 1.05rem;
		line-height: 1.65;
		color: var(--color-sepia);
		margin: 0 0 1.5rem 0;
	}

	.btn-support {
		display: inline-block;
		padding: 0.95rem 2rem;
		font-family: var(--font-body);
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		letter-spacing: 0.06em;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		text-decoration: none;
		color: var(--color-ink);
		background: var(--color-cream);
		border: 2px solid var(--color-sand-dark);
		border-radius: 50px;
		box-shadow: 0 2px 14px rgba(30, 122, 122, 0.2);
		transition: transform 0.25s ease, box-shadow 0.25s ease, background 0.2s ease;
	}

	.btn-support:hover {
		transform: translateY(-2px);
		background: #fff;
		box-shadow: 0 6px 22px rgba(30, 122, 122, 0.28);
	}

	/* --- Final CTA --- */
	.cta-section {
		background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--color-foam) 0%, var(--color-sand) 100%);
		padding: 4rem 2rem;
		text-align: center;
	}

	.btn-schedule {
		display: inline-block;
		padding: 1rem 2.25rem;
		font-family: var(--font-body);
		font-size: 1rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		letter-spacing: 0.08em;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		text-decoration: none;
		color: var(--color-cream);
		background: var(--color-sand-dark);
		border-radius: 50px;
		box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(30,122,122,0.35);
		transition: transform 0.25s ease, box-shadow 0.25s ease;
	}

	.btn-schedule:hover {
		transform: translateY(-3px);
		box-shadow: 0 8px 28px rgba(30,122,122,0.45);
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.hero-long {
			min-height: 60vh;
			padding: 2rem 1rem;
		}
		.hero-long-title {
			font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 10vw, 3.5rem);
		}
		.hero-long-subtitle {
			font-size: clamp(0.9rem, 3vw, 1rem);
		}
		.hero-long-tagline {
			font-size: clamp(0.95rem, 2.5vw, 1.1rem);
		}
		.reunion-section {
			padding: 2.5rem 1rem;
		}
		.reunion-container {
			gap: 1.5rem;
		}
		.reunion-body {
			font-size: 1rem;
			max-width: none;
		}
		.reunion-tagline {
			font-size: 1rem;
			max-width: none;
		}
		.reunion-poster {
			max-width: 100%;
		}
		.reunion-poster-btn {
			min-height: 48px;
			padding: 0.85rem 1.25rem;
			font-size: 0.9rem;
		}
		.calendar-callout {
			padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
		}
		.calendar-callout-dates {
			font-size: 1.1rem;
		}
		.hansen-section {
			padding: 4rem 1rem;
		}
		.hansen-photo-frame {
			float: none;
			width: 100%;
			margin: 0 0 2rem 0;
			text-align: center;
		}
		.hansen-photo {
			max-width: 300px;
			margin: 0 auto;
			box-shadow: 10px 10px 0px var(--color-sand);
		}
		.hansen-heading {
			font-size: 2rem;
		}
		.support-section {
			padding: 2.5rem 1rem;
		}
		.support-text {
			font-size: 1rem;
		}
		.btn-support {
			min-height: 48px;
			padding: 0.85rem 1.75rem;
			font-size: 0.88rem;
		}
		.cta-section {
			padding: 2.5rem 1rem;
		}
		.btn-schedule {
			min-height: 48px;
			padding: 0.9rem 1.5rem;
			font-size: 0.9rem;
		}
	}

	@media (max-width: 640px) {
		.reunion-container {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			gap: 1.25rem;
		}
		.reunion-section {
			padding: 2rem 1rem;
		}
		.hansen-section {
			padding: 3rem 1rem;
		}
		.support-section,
		.cta-section {
			padding: 2rem 1rem;
		}
		.calendar-callout-dates {
			font-size: 1rem;
		}
	}
</style>
